{"type": "article", "id": 43787, "title": "草帽戴得好，绝对是个造型加分项｜这个设计了不起", "description": "每个周末，《好奇心日报》都会找个主题为你寻找精彩设计。", "date": "2017-08-04T23:33:55Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1531, "name": "帽子"}, {"id": 43000, "name": "Eugenia Kim"}, {"id": 43001, "name": "Kijima Takayuki"}, {"id": 43002, "name": "Lack Of Color"}, {"id": 43003, "name": "Override"}, {"id": 43004, "name": "Janessa Leoné"}, {"id": 43005, "name": "Lock & Co. Hatters"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 179, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170805000005RBSHVIAoaO1Dyhg2.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p3 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p4 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p5 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} p.p6 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p7 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333; min-height: 25.0px} p.p8 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 12.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #323333} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} span.s2 {font-kerning: none; color: #363636} span.s3 {font-kerning: none; color: #323333} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。<br></p><p>对抗烈日高温，除了<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/30676.html\">墨镜</a>之外，少不了一顶遮阳草帽。每到夏天，很多品牌都会推出以经典的巴拿马帽为首的帽款。本周的推荐就是这些还能为整体穿搭加分的帽子。</p><h3>Eugenia Kim</h3><p>与创始人同名的 <a href=\"http://www.eugeniakim.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eugenia Kim</a> 最初只是一个女帽品牌：1998 年，因为发型没剪好，Kim 不得不为自己设计了一顶羽毛钟型帽，没想到很快就因为独特的设计风格被纽约高端百货商店巴尼斯（Barneys）相中，最终得以创立。Kim 尤其擅长将经典的款式与有趣的元素结合在一起，很能彰显佩戴者的个性，比如宽帽檐上带有“do not disturb”（勿扰）之类台词的涂鸦款就曾在 Instagram 上刷屏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000044rYed7mtugiojLlWa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000044kjxswCvUiF7qfTGb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708050000443MbhIaHYSK5rtfB6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000045MV1HP40xRhD3O2Sr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Kijima Takayuki</h3><p>1995 年，师从日本制帽大师平田晓夫的木岛隆幸和妻子木岛道子成立了名为 <a href=\"http://coeur-chapeau.jp/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Coeur</a> 帽子品牌，<a href=\"http://www.kijimatakayuki.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Kijima Takayuki</a> 则是木岛隆幸于 2013 年从 Coeur 独立出来的品牌。以“在简约的装扮中占据存在感”为设计理念，Kijima Takayuki 依靠全手工打造、对材料的考究和针对亚洲人头型修改的款式成为话题品牌。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708050001011HoWx0G6D43zurpA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.826027\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708050001002ShrYxRNdvGJlHoQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.708219\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000100KRUH5IXtmb1Nh2yo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665753\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000100tiHce4E17wFN9TMW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.671233\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lack Of Color</h3><p>来自澳大利亚昆士兰州的 <a href=\"https://lack-of-color.myshopify.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lack Of Color</a> 是由 Tess Corvaia 和 Robert Tilbury 这对制帽匠情侣创立于 2011 年的品牌，高性价比（大部分在 100 澳元以下）和丰富的款式甚至得到了包括超模 Gigi Hadid 和时尚博主 Chiara Ferragni 等人的青睐。2017 年夏季系列 <a href=\"https://www.lackofcolor.com.au/blogs/collections/canyons-summer-18\" rel=\"nofollow\">Canyons</a> 主打充满夏日感的编织草帽，其中有一部分还特意邀请来自多米尼加的制帽匠打造。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000334qAPnl240NHZhOuWK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.509000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000334HqmgOBQaZRCl45Sz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662691\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000334NOsSy5EAhJgYTeoR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662691\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000335kGJKih7Fcp39RxD2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.509000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Override</h3><p><a href=\"http://overridehat.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Override</a> 是一个基于日本特有的帽子文化而创立的品牌，原创设计都围绕“Sense of Japan”这一主题而展开，重视“感性”、“感觉”和“感动”这三个概念，对素材、缝制以及舒适度都非常讲究。每到夏季，由经过特殊处理的和纸编织而成的帽子就会因为容易折叠、透气性佳的特性得到追捧。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000143OYw43IFqptiZf8or.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.645679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201708050001226zPu7yoZOeWRvQTC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.645679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000122eS2VYAHK796iI84c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.645679\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000123nmol1kj6iCrNGJzO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.645679\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Janessa Leoné</h3><p>作为意大利移民的后裔，现居洛杉矶的 <a href=\"https://janessaleone.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Janessa Leoné</a> 自幼就与帽子结下了不解之缘。回忆中一直戴着帽子的祖父以及<a href=\"http://www.latimes.com/fashion/la-ig-janessa-leone-20151220-story.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">无意间发现的一顶复古软呢帽</a>促使她在 2013 年创立了同名女帽品牌，致力于通过设计重现那个用帽子体现个人品味并将其传承下去的时代。Leoné 延续了意大利手工制帽的传统，看起来硬挺简约，不会给人太过张扬的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000200wh7QLaJMdO3ZCTUN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000201PKFBsm3W78wbkfSC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000201pgfMcdeiXj81a2yr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000201a6yFYb19cM0dOutf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.425000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Lock &amp; Co. Hatters</h3><p>现存最古老家族企业之一、成立于 1676 年的 <a href=\"http://www.lockhatters.co.uk/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lock &amp; Co. Hatters</a> 是世界上最古老的帽子店。尽管它从 1993 年开始经营女帽的高级定制，它还是以传统男帽最为出名，并且获得过来自菲利普亲王和查尔斯王子的皇室认证。入夏以来，巴拿马帽就在官方网站上占据了醒目的位置，这些轻便优雅的帽子均由巴拿马帽发源地厄瓜多尔的工匠手工制作而成。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000219VBoKAw5sTPcYxENX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000220uoCpTErMxWA45BPZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000219LTODoE7zG6RQnHjU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170805000220rqXC36WQMA0pDnx8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}